atching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bf91d9e8a82d0e2f6e7ca4803b9cf75da6b16e40","tid":1630961,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"頭先紅隧見到 去大丸要20蚊<br />\n唔好搭 一蚊都唔好俾佢地賺"},{"pid":"32c76e54b7cebbfb72d2510a0046bc5a1f8b296f","tid":1630961,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"10加到20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a04f093628b53343a19d90ac2d40d4a0226781","tid":1630961,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdf323833de0659a0e5f52164dfdf0b435ef6aa","tid":1630961,"uid":64264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0ff6e36582f1028ff631b047184eb5c142b110","tid":1630961,"uid":53673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94304cd6da3495e46da1a726d76a4b3bf6f6a76c","tid":1630961,"uid":64264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 旺角返元朗要$100<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小巴佬死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji